name: VENOMOUS SOCIETY
description:
Often we think that a situation and environment filled with peace and comfort is something we want in life. Comfort zone!

But we are not aware, actually it is like a poisonous snake that creeps calmly towards us, ready to prey on us slowly with its very subtle and deadly venom.

Seize the great opportunities of our future in the cradle of short comforts. Devouring freedom explores our passions. Gripping cruelly on our warrior identity that ends with a future so bleak as sour fruit at the end of a delicious meal.

'Comfort Zone' is life's detention!

.

Digital Illustration | Photoshop | 3000 x 3000 px | 300 ppi
Agus Setyawan | @angoes25 | 2021
